    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make pay rises in line with inflation a condition of all Government contracts",
        "additional_details": "We tax payers fund these massive government contracts. In a cost of living crisis, employers must act responsibly, especially with public money. There is no room for increasing profits when too many staff are on the bread line.",
        "background": "Make it a condition of contract that companies pay annual inflationary pay rises to hard working staff rather than seeking to maximise profits.",
